(177, 32, 'theories', 'Supposed ‘truth tellers’ claim that there is evidence that Stevie has been pretending to be blind all these years – although they have given no explanation for why he might want to do such a thing, the Metro reports. Such ‘evidence’ cited in the conspiracy blogs includes the fact that Stevie often enjoys sitting in the front row at basketball games, as well as the time earlier this year when he seemed to look down to read the winner from an envelope at the Grammys.'),
